title: Los Angeles Clippers, Cleveland Browns, Cam Newton and Ezekiel Elliot
itunes:title: Los Angeles Clippers, Cleveland Browns, Cam Newton and Ezekiel Elliot
description:
Colin explains why the pressure is on the Los Angeles Clippers and the Cleveland Browns, proof he was always right about Carolina Panthers QB Cam Newton, and an update on Dallas Cowboys RB Ezekiel Elliot. 

Guests include: Chris Haynes, Geoff Schwartz, Sam Monson, and Rashad Jennings.
